The 2nd Annual LNG USA Summit will take place on February 27-28, 2018 in Houston, Texas. The Summit speakers and panelists will discuss the challenges and opportunities in the LNG industry and what new exciting projects are looming. The event also facilitates the building of valuable partnerships by providing ample time for socializing and private business meetings. LNG professionals, business executives and industry leaders from NextDecade, Black & Veatch, LNG Limited, Monkey Island LNG, Repsol, CH2M, Crowley and much more will gather together for two days of important discussions, informative conversations and countless business growth opportunities. https://www.lng-usa.com/ Venue: Hyatt Regency North Houston, 425 North Sam Houston Parkway East, Houston, Texas, USA, 77060.